# rx_negpi4 — Rx(-π/4) = e^{i(π/8)X}. Pauli-X 지수 회전(TFIM 가로장 항). analytic golden.
```python id=bloq
import numpy as np
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Rx
bloq = Rx(-np.pi/4)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
X = np.array([[0,1],[1,0]], complex)
golden = (np.cos(np.pi/8)*np.eye(2) + 1j*np.sin(np.pi/8)*X).astype(complex)
```
